Surfing festival to be held in Karnataka.
Come May, and Karnataka Tourism will host its first-ever surfing festival. In a bid to dub Karnataka as a tourist hub, the state's tourism ministry is introducing a set of recreational activities that can be enjoyed by those interested. According to a report by the Indian Express, The Indian Open of Surfing, will take place between May 27 to May 29 at the Sasithithlu Beach in Mangaluru. 